                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340703-42-victim341 t18340703-42-viclabel227"></join>. The prisoner was in my employ - he manufactured goods for me- brought the work home, and <rs id="t18340703-42-deflabel228" type="occupation">took goods out and sold them - he was entrusted to receive monies</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340703-42-defend340 t18340703-42-deflabel228"></join> for me.</p>
